</para>
</refsect1>

<refsect1>
<title>Examples</title>

<literallayout>
&lt;IfModule mod_load.c&gt;
MaxLoad                 10 "Access denied, server load too high"
&lt;/IfModule&gt;
</literallayout>

<para>
FIXFIX
</para>

</refsect1>
